<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>The Zend_Auth_Adapter_Http class contains an error on line 535:</p>

<pre class="highlight"><code>
        $creds = array_filter(explode(':', $auth));
</code></pre>

<p>When a password contains a :, this will be rendered broken.</p>

<p>The line should better be:</p>

<pre class="highlight"><code>
        $creds = array_filter(explode(':', $auth, 2));
</code></pre>

